'''史蒂芬·布雷克·克勞德'''（{{lang-en|'''Steven Blake Crowder'''}}，{{bd|1987年|7月7日}}）是[[美國|美國]]的一位演員、喜劇演員和保守派政治評論員。他是Louder with Crowder的主持人<ref>{{cite web|url=http://louderwithcrowder.com|title=Homepage » Louder With Crowder|publisher=|accessdate=2020-10-03|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926204426/https://www.louderwithcrowder.com/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，並且曾長期在[[福斯新聞頻道|福斯新聞頻道]]出演<ref name="Big Journalism">{{cite web|url=http://www.breitbart.com/Big-Journalism/2013/10/22/Fox-News-Steven-Crowder|title=Exclusive–Fox News: Steven Crowder Attacking Hannity Confirms 'Decision to Part Company with Him'|accessdate=20 December 2013|archive-date=2017-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170120181836/http://www.breitbart.com/big-journalism/2013/10/22/fox-news-steven-crowder/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。克勞德出生在格罗斯波因特。2009年之後，克勞德開始定期在保守媒體上出演。2011年他擔任[[保守政治行動會議|保守政治行動會議]]的主持。<ref>{{cite web | title = CPAC 2011: Schedule of events | url = http://www.conservative.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/SCHEDULE-OF-EVENTS-MASTER-2-4-11WEB.pdf | format = PDF | publisher = [[Conservative_Political_Action_Conference|Conservative Political Action Conference]] | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120916222958/http://www.conservative.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/SCHEDULE-OF-EVENTS-MASTER-2-4-11WEB.pdf | archivedate = 2012-09-16 | accessdate = 2016-12-23 }}</ref>。2021年6月22日，與知名Podcast主持人Ethan Klein於其節目H3 Podcast進行政治辯論時，因害怕與著名政治評論家Sam Seder辯論而臨陣脫逃，因而有了新綽號Steven "Coward"。<ref>{{cite web | title = Ethan Klein Debates Steven Crowder (Ft. Sam Seder) - H3 Podcast | url = https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fvg5RTrFLfI | publisher = [[H3_Podcast|H3 Podcast]] | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2021-06-23 | archive-date = 2022-03-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220322144539/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fvg5RTrFLfI }}</ref>。

